  "text": "Complete type family trace for FxVanillaOption across OpenGamma Strata:\n\n## Core Domain Classes (Product Module - modules/product/)\nThe 4 Joda-Beans domain classes for FxVanillaOption are located in com.opengamma.strata.product.fxopt package:\n1. FxVanillaOption - Base FX vanilla option product class representing the core option contract\n2. FxVanillaOptionTrade - Trade wrapper around FxVanillaOption, representing a trading instance with counterparty and settlement info\n3. ResolvedFxVanillaOption - Resolved form of FxVanillaOption with all references resolved\n4. ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade - Resolved form of FxVanillaOptionTrade with all references resolved\n\n## Pricer Classes (Pricer Module - modules/pricer/)\nThe pricing implementations are located in com.opengamma.strata.pricer.fxopt package and use two pricing models (Black and Vanna-Volga), each with ProductPricer and TradePricer variants:\n1. BlackFxVanillaOptionProductPricer - Prices ResolvedFxVanillaOption using Black's lognormal model\n2. BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer - Prices ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade using Black's lognormal model, wraps the product pricer\n3. VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionProductPricer - Prices ResolvedFxVanillaOption using the Vanna-Volga smile model\n4. VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer - Prices ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade using Vanna-Volga model, wraps the product pricer\n\nNote: No Normal model or Implied-Tree pricers exist for FxVanillaOption in the codebase. Only Black and Vanna-Volga models are implemented.\n\n## Measure Calculation Classes (Measure Module - modules/measure/)\nThe calculation engine integration classes are located in com.opengamma.strata.measure.fxopt package:\n1. FxVanillaOptionMeasureCalculations - Core calculations that compute PV, sensitivities, and Greeks using the pricers\n2. FxVanillaOptionMethod - Enum defining available pricing methods (Black, VannaVolga)\n3. FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculationFunction - Calculation function implementation for the RFR framework\n4. FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculations - Wrapper for measure calculations that coordinates with pricers and market data\n\n## CSV Loader (Loader Module - modules/loader/)\nThe trade loader for CSV import:\n1. FxVanillaOptionTradeCsvPlugin (modules/loader/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/loader/csv/) - Parses FX vanilla option trades from CSV format, handles premium dates, strikes, currencies, and settlement information\n\n## Dependency Embedding (Product Module - modules/product/)\nThe barrier option that depends on FxVanillaOption:\n1. FxSingleBarrierOption (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/) - FX single barrier option that embeds FxVanillaOption as its underlyingOption field. This class represents knock-in and knock-out options on top of vanilla FX options, adding barrier terms and optional rebate amounts.\n\n## Type Family Relationships\n- FxVanillaOption is the base product type\n- FxVanillaOptionTrade wraps FxVanillaOption with trade metadata\n- Both resolve to Resolved* versions that bind to market data\n- Pricing flows through specialized *Pricer classes (Black and Vanna-Volga models)\n- Measure calculations wire pricers to the calculation framework\n- FxSingleBarrierOption composes FxVanillaOption as its underlying asset\n- CSV loader enables trade import/export functionality"
}

